main.headline: Google
main.name: Developer Students' Club
main.description: The coolest community of coders trying to make some cool stuff
main.bio: Google's Developer Student Club is a student club for University of Melbourne students who want to learn a wide range of valuable, technical skills such as Machine Learning, Android Development etc. and join an amazing network of like minded developers.
